THIS IS A VERSION WITH MORE FEATURES WITH GMOD FROM "http://gaddons.org/". I DO NOT OWN ANY RIGHTS, I ONLY PUT MORE ADDONS AND CONTENTS IN THIS GMOD.

INSTALLATION:

Only extract the Gary's Mod folder anywhere. Click on START.BAT to run the game.
To change your Player name open the LumaEmu.ini in ther Gary's Mod folder and in: [Player]
PlayerName = Player
Only change "Player" to your name, like:
[Player]
PlayerName = YourNameHere
